curl -XPOST 'http://localhost:9200/electronic_products/_create/1800' -H 'Content-Type: application/json' -d '{"product_name": "SGM38042B-1/SGM38042B-3/SGM38042B-5", "table_name": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION", "content": "GENERAL DESCRIPTION  The SGM38042B-1, SGM38042B-3 and SGM38042B-5  generate both positive and negative precision regulated  voltage power sources with a control scheme for single  inductor dual output converter. The positive output is  programmable from 2.4V to 6.4V with 100mV per step,  and the negative output is programmable from -2V to  -3.2V with 50mV per step.  A linear regulator capable of 50mA output current is  also integrated. These devices are equipped with  1-Wire interface. With input in the range of 2.7V to 5.5V,  these devices are optimized for loading 100mA in  boost-inverter mode and also work in buck-inverter  mode.  The SGM38042B-1/3/5 are available in a Green  WLCSP-1.51×2.10-15B package. They operate over  an ambient temperature range of -40℃ to +85℃.    "}'
